summary: An ordinance amending Section 1 of Ordinance No. 45196, entitled: "An ordinance relating to and providing for the condemnation, appropriation and taking of certain lands and other property in blocks 5 and 7, respectively, King County Addition to the City of Seattle, for park purposes, and providing that payment for the same be made from the General Fund of the City of Seattle", approved June 4, 1923.
